<FONT SIZE=4>
<FONT SIZE=+10>I</FONT> am a second year masters student at 
<!WA6><IMG SRC="http://www.cs.mcgill.ca/~vola/images/mcgill.gif">Mcgill university, studying under 
the Computer Science departement.  My thesis work is oriented toward 
the use of of robotics to create image-based virtual reality environments.  
For more information on my work please follow this link 
	<!WA7><A HREF="http://www.mcrcim.mcgill.ca/~ciaravola/"> 
